The Azure Iris is a tiny inn adjoining the Fortune's Wheel, used as an exclusive hotel for high-ups who have had too much to drink or as a suite for shadowy business dealings.
The Azure Iris is run by a wood elf from the world of Oerth by the name of Verden. 

